text:
Aur missu Dhep! 
Bhai first year tk toh mein bs tujhe aise hi jaanta tha ki hmari wing ka ek banda hai jo wing se zyada baki wings mein zyada rehta haiğŸ˜‚.phir 2nd year se jb tu Ritesh ka roomie bna toh uske baad se hmari baatein shuru hui.uske baad toh jb bhi tere saath jata canteen kbhi 1ghnte se pehle ni aatağŸ˜‚.baki tera chillana bhot yaad aayega abhi bhi bokaro mein chillata hai toh punjab awaaz aati hai ğŸ˜‚.Aur ek baat yaad rkhna carrom,football,cards mein tu bachcha hi rhega ğŸ˜›.

text:
Hellooo Saransh!
Bhot accha lga yr tumse aur riya se milkr.Never expected ki itte km time main itni acchi friendship ho jaayegi.baki chanda mama se lekr ğŸ˜¨ ye vaale emoji tk toh atishay ne raaz khol hi diya haiğŸ˜….trip pe tum logon ke saath bhot maza aaya aur uss din peene ke baad sambhalne ke liye shukriya. phir campus mein UNO khelna,cards khelne,late night talks toh maine most of the times miss hi kiğŸ˜….Looking forward to a trip with you guys soon,till then all the best and take care :)

text:
Aur bhai 4D!
Mujhe lgta hai itni toh Doraemon ki pocket famous ni hui thi jitna teri 4D famous ho gyi hai ğŸ˜‚.Vo Wasim ki class mein ludo khelne se lekr organic chemistry ke course tk pta hi ni chla yr ye 2 saal kb nikl gye.
Patte khelna,ludo khelna,daaru party,momos khana aur the most important PUBG khelna(vo toh chlo chlti thi aur chlti rhegi) sab kiya bs padai chodkrğŸ˜‚.

text:
Aur bhai shukla!
Bhaiyon ko chodkr tu hi tha jo mera pehla dost bna tha campus mein.uske baad toh bs phir roz raat ko canteen jana ho,raat ko rolls khane oat jana ho,late night talks,phir tere raat ke mood swings ko sambhalna hoğŸ˜‚.yaad hai ek raat jb doaa gye they paidal aur library ke paas kitte pr gye they piche kya toh phti thi yr.yaad hai 2nd year ki antragni toh pubg khelte nikali.ek hi baat ka dukh rhega tere saath trip miss ho gya.bhot maza aaya yr inn 4 saalon mein.abhi iss saal tu bhi acchi c placement le aur aaja apni city hi.
Jldi hi milenge.

text:
Aur bhai Dinesh!
1st year mein toh hum zyada ek dusre ko nhi jaante they kyunki tu hugge ke us taraf rehta tha pr lgta hai shayad tu bhool gya vo 2md year hi toh tha jb hum mini militia,pubg khela krte they.Aur haan football ko toh kaise hi bhool skte hai raat ko 2-3 bje tk khelte rehnağŸ˜.pta ni ab kb khelna hoga yrğŸ˜­.Aur yr trip pe toh kya hi maze kiye vo haridwar mein baba ka prasad bhot mehnga pdh gya thağŸ˜‚.Aur ye last ka mahina toh gajab hi tha bhai,raat raat bhar mafia khelna,patte khelna,ganja,daaru party aur vo MT mein jaakr katwana apnağŸ˜….Ab toh bs yr tu Japan jaakr mujhe bhi bula lena issi bahane japan bhi ghoom lenge.Aur main toh bulana nhi bhoolunga pr agr tu na aaya toh bhot peetega dekhna.
author: Rahul  Jindal

text:
Aur bhaiyyyy pandeyyyy! ! 
 Mujhe yaad hai hum pehli baar TA202 mein mile they.vahan toh TA202 ke project ke ilawa zyada baatein ni ho paati pr yr ye 30 din jo guzre,vo tera roz ka wing mein ghoomte phirna bhai sutta hai sutta haiğŸ˜‚,bhookh lg rhi ,cards khelna subah tk breakfast ke liye jagna aise lgta tha jaise first year ke dost ho.dekhte hai abhi kya aati hai job location banglore aayi toh pelte hai yr vahan bakchodi.
author: Rahul  Jindal

text:
Aur bhai Ram!
Haan yr hum khandu ke through hi mile they.uske baad toh fir yr online semester mein macroeconomics ki quiz bs baatein krne ke bahane theyğŸ˜‚.Aur yr mereko toh sochte hue bhi darr lgta hai agr tu na hota quarantine ke time toh mera kya hota.kahan phir swiggy order hotağŸ˜…. quarantine ke baad toh yr f3 mein pde rehna maal fukna, daaru peena,aur 3 patti.Tera vo 1 hi puff mein bhand ho jaana aur bhand hokr v shape raaton pe nikl jaanağŸ˜‚.bhot maje kiye.yr tere saath.milte hai yr jld hi.

text:
Aur bhai Ritesh!
Tere baare mein toh jitna bolu utna km hai yr.hum pehli baar physics ke tutorial mein mile they jb midden ke papers baant rhi thi tutor, vaise hi phti pdhi thi aur tujhse alg se himmat mil rhi thi jb tu keh rha tera bhi accha ni hua.vo alg baat hia vo bs 2 min ki hi thi himmat(samajh toh gya hi hoga tu)ğŸ˜‚ uske baad se toh yr phir chahe end sems ke liye padhna ho, koi bhi apni baatein share krni ho, football khelna ,phir chahe placement ke liye madad krni ho,tu best partner tha yr.aise hi na thodi na hmein love birds bolte theyğŸ˜‚.Aur vo mussoorie ki trip kaise bhool skte hai jahan choona lg wake kr aaye theyğŸ˜‚.bs ab ek hi baat ka dukh hai yr tu ab hyderabad ja rha aur hmara banglore mein football khelna ka plan reh gyağŸ˜­.Ab lgta hai mujhe hi hyderabad aakr khelni pdhegi football.

text: Aur bhai motu(past ke liye).ab toh apne bhai ne dieting shuru kr di hai(fitness pro).hmari trip ka mastermind aur money bankğŸ˜‚.yaad hai George everest  jaate time tera bolte phirna thoda rukte hai na abhi thak gye hai.aur yr 2nd year ki summer mein jo roz shaam ko chat khane jana,phir hall 1 ki canteen.aur ipl mein teri opposite team ko cheer krne mein bhot maza aata tha aur aata rhega.

text:
Kaun tang kr rha hai yr! Yhi reaction tha mera jb tumhara pehli baar call aaya tha(so rha tha na)ğŸ˜….uske baad toh phir classes ke gotte marna yahan tk ki labs tk ke gotte marna kya kuch ni kiya yr in 2 saalon mein(ofcourse except padhai).bhand ho jana ,tumhare hall ki pyaz MaggieğŸ˜,Wasim ki class mein ludo khelna,class mein rough copies bharna,choti khichnağŸ˜….bhot masti ki yr ye 2 saalon mein.Aur kuch aisi baatein chahkr bhi nhi bhool skta vo tumhara goa ki trip pe ghar ka room freshner le aanağŸ˜‚ğŸ˜‚,OAT ki chatt pr kikli pauni,aur tumahar reaction jis din tumhe bed se chot lg gyi thiğŸ˜‚.Aur haan ek complain yr PUBG main abhi tk ni sikhaya mujhe 10 finger 10 toe se khelna itna talent rkh kr kya kroge thoda sa idhar bhi baant doğŸ˜‚ğŸ˜‚.Baki apni toh PUBG chlti hi rhegi kyunki revive krne vaala bhi toh koi chahiyeğŸ˜›.

Jb pehli baar kmre mein aaya tha tu toh lga tha bhai ye kaun aa gya pdhaku baccha.phir pta lga ye toh apni hi breed haiğŸ˜‚.1st year toh yr phir aisa hi nikala hai chl roll order krte hai,chl anime dekhte hai,aur sabse main chl Sanjay ki lete haiğŸ˜‚.Aur sbse main point jo aaj tk chl rha(chl WWE krte hai).kya majje kiye hai yr vo alg baat hai 2nd year se tu thoda zyada hi pdhaku bachcha bn gya tha(chaapu in coding).Ab toh apna bhai smart bhi ho gya hai.tere se toh milna hota rhega kahin bhi jaunga toh delhi hokr hi jaunga bs tu bed ka intezaam karke rkhna agla WWE delhi mein hi hoga.
